description: After his second loss on NK, Paul Wagner returns looking more muscular and sexier than ever. In preparation for the match, he has been working on his skills and has been observing the local wrestling club practices. His opponent this week is two time winner, Sebastian Keys. Sebastian has earned three black belts in Martial Arts and has been known to be very calm and focused on the mat. Paul is tired of losing and intends to use his aggression and size to slam his opponent to the mat and rank up points. This strategy doesn't bother Sebastian at all, because he intends to use Paul's size to his advantage. The bigger they are the harder they fall. Someone is going to get tossed around the mat and fucked hard this week.
title: Sebastian Keys vs Paul Wagner
